FBIS3-23307 "jptot011__l94123" JPRS-TOT-94-011-L Document Type:JPRS Document Title:Terrorism FOUO 11 March 1994 CENTRAL EURASIA RUSSIA Irkust Airport Closed, Search for Bomb Under Way LD1103071294 Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service in Russian 0626 GMT 11 Mar 94 LD1103071294 Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service Language: Russian Article Type:BFN [Text] Irkutsk, 11 Mar -- At this time Irkutsk airport is closed: a search is going on in the building for an explosive device. The ITAR-TASS correspondent learned at 1300 hours local time today that a phone call was made by an unidentified individual to the main militia department of the city of Irkutsk, reporting that the airport building was mined. The passengers and staff were evacuated.
